content = pd.DataFrame([wthr.HourlyWeatherReport(lat=self.lat, lon=self.lon,
    date=(self.day - dt.timedelta(days=i)).date(), time=self.time).dict for
    i in range(2)])
wthr.put_to_cache(content, self.session)
t = self.session.query(wthr.HourlyWeatherReport).all()
self.assertTrue(len(t) == 2)
for i in range(2):
    t = wthr.get_from_cache(date=self.day - dt.timedelta(days=i), lat=self.
        lat, lon=self.lon, session=self.session)
    self.assertTrue(isinstance(t, pd.DataFrame))
    self.assertTrue(len(t) == 1)
